{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078470/extras/description_banner_03.png?t=1737762788\" />Smol Survivors is a 2D reverse bullet-heck where smol blocks have become lost and need to find their friends and a way back home while fighting through hordes of enemies.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What can I do to make sure I stay safe?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect weapons and upgrade them using enemy essence</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase badges to modify aspects of combat using coins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find other blocks using the gacha system</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Okay, how do I do any of that?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Weapons can be collected and upgraded during combat at no extra cost</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on urgent quests from the quest board to find and bring back important lost blocks that will lend you their services</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Save up enough money to take a spin at Capsule's gacha shop</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sounds easy enough, anything else I should know?</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When in doubt, complete an expedition in the most recently discovered area</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There's bigger and badder things beyond the portal that we've labeled as &quot;bosses.&quot; These will need to be dealt with to proceed at times.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">That sounds dangerous...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yup it sure is! But it's okay, because you're a Smol Survivor.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078470/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737762788","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078470/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737762